WEBVTT

00:04.566 --> 00:07.433
MISS CACCIATORE, YOUR GUIDANCE
COUNSELOR HERE INFORMS ME

00:07.499 --> 00:09.998
THAT YOU ENTERED MY UNIVERSITY
TWO MONTHS AGO

00:10.066 --> 00:11.698
