MY GUIDANCE COUNSELOR IS A DICK.

00:17.532 --> 00:18.332
[ SIGHS ]

00:18.399 --> 00:21.232
YOU´RE PRE-MED, YET YOU HAVEN´T
ATTENDED A SINGLE LAB.

00:21.299 --> 00:22.531
