A LITTLE REMINDER

00:37.532 --> 00:41.598
OF WHAT THIS UNIVERSITY
IS REALLY ABOUT.

00:43.299 --> 00:44.598
CHECK THIS OUT.

00:44.666 --> 00:46.166
[ LAUGHS ]

00:46.232 --> 00:49.031
MOVIES!
I LOVE MOVIES.

00:51.732 --> 00:55.565
♪  DEEP WITHIN THE MOUNTAINS
OF BLUE  ♪

00:55.632 --> 00:59.065
♪  THERE´S A UNIVERSITY
THAT´S PERFECT FOR YOU  ♪

00:59.132 --> 01:02.264
♪  WHERE EDUCATION
IS PRIORITY ONE  ♪

01:02.332 --> 01:06.132
♪  GET A MAJOR IN KNOWLEDGE
