I AM B.M.S.

01:16.666 --> 01:20.099
♪  B.M.S., B.M.S.  ♪

01:20.166 --> 01:22.632
♪  WHO IS B.M.S.?  ♪

01:22.699 --> 01:24.931
WE ARE B.M.S.

01:24.999 --> 01:26.566
I AM B.M.S.

01:26.632 --> 01:29.132
HI.
I´M DEAN SIMON.

01:29.199 --> 01:32.698
ENROLL NOW AND SCORE
A TOUCHDOWN IN EDUCATION.

01:37.399 --> 01:40.199
♪  B.M.S., B.M.S.  ♪

01:40.266 --> 01:44.365
♪  YOU ARE B.M.S.  ♪

01:46.032 --> 01:48.165
[ SIGHS ]
GOD, THAT WAS GOOD.

01:48.232 --> 01:50.264
I GUESS WHAT I´M SAYING,
MISS CACCIATORE,

01:50.332 --> 01:53.431
IS THAT THE TIME HAS COME
TO STEP UP OR --

01:53.499 --> 01:55.098
MISS CACCIATORE!

01:55.166 --> 01:56.698
I JUST HAVE TO PEE REAL QUICK.

01:56.766 --> 01:58.098
[ URINATING ]

01:58.166 --> 02:00.265
[ REV THEORY´S "HELL YEAH"
PLAYS ]

02:00.332 --> 02:01.531
CAN YOU FEEL THAT?

02:04.566 --> 02:06.133
YOU BETTER HOLD ON.

02:06.199 --> 02:08.331
THIS ONE´S ABOUT TO GET BUMPY.

02:09.299 --> 02:11.065
♪ GIVE ME A "HELL" ♪

02:11.132 --> 02:12.098
♪ GIVE ME A "YEAH" ♪

02:12.166 --> 02:13.032
♪ HELL, YEAH ♪

02:13.099 --> 02:14.966
♪ STAND UP RIGHT NOW ♪

02:15.032 --> 02:16.432
♪ GIVE ME A "HELL" ♪

02:16.499 --> 02:18.665
♪ GIVE ME A "YEAH" ♪

02:18.732 --> 02:20.165
♪ STAND UP RIGHT NOW ♪

02:20.232 --> 02:22.031
♪ GIVE ME A "HELL" ♪

02:22.099 --> 02:24.366
♪ GIVE ME A "YEAH" ♪

02:24.432 --> 02:26.731
♪ STAND UP RIGHT NOW ♪

02:30.466 --> 02:32.598
SOMEONE DRINK WITH ME!
COME ON!

02:32.666 --> 02:33.499
I´M IN.

02:33.566 --> 02:34.932
YES.

02:34.999 --> 02:36.999
MARY JO, WHY AREN´T YOU
DRINKING WITH HIM?

02:37.066 --> 02:39.933
SOME DEAN GUY
PUT ME ON ACADEMIC PROBATION.

02:39.999 --> 02:42.031
WAIT.
THEY HAVE THAT HERE?

02:42.099 --> 02:42.999
APPARENTLY.

02:43.066 --> 02:44.533
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

02:44.599 --> 02:46.332
I GOT IT.

02:48.399 --> 02:50.498
HOMEWORK DELIVERY
FOR ALEX MORAN.

02:50.566 --> 02:52.132
WHAT´D YOU SAY, GLASSES?

02:52.199 --> 02:53.165
I´M HAVING TROUBLE HEARING YOU

02:53.232 --> 02:55.098
THROUGH THOSE THICK GLASSES,
GLASSES.

02:55.166 --> 02:57.199
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.
COME ON. HEY.

02:57.266 --> 02:58.199
THANKS, GARY.

02:58.266 --> 02:59.465
WHAT I WOULD DO WITHOUT YOU?

02:59.532 --> 03:00.598
LEARN SOMETHING.

03:00.666 --> 03:02.666
WHOA!
YOU GIVING HIM SASS, GLASSES?

03:02.732 --> 03:03.665
´CAUSE I´LL BREAK
YOUR GODDAMN --

03:03.732 --> 03:05.499
OKAY, YEAH.
APPRECIATE IT.

03:05.566 --> 03:07.098
WHAT IS WRONG WITH YOU?

03:07.166 --> 03:08.599
-WHAT IS WRONG WITH ME?
-YEAH.

03:08.666 --> 03:10.165
THAT NERD´S A NERD, MAN.

03:10.232 --> 03:12.232
JOCKS LIKE US
DON´T TALK TO NERDS.

03:12.299 --> 03:13.331
WE PRANK THEM.

03:13.399 --> 03:15.366
SAMMY, YOU´RE NOT A JOCK.

03:15.432 --> 03:17.265
GOOD ONE.
I´M NOT A JOCK.

03:17.332 --> 03:18.764
WHO´S PRANKING WHO NOW?

03:20.466 --> 03:22.333
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

03:22.399 --> 03:24.465
EXCUSE ME.

03:24.532 --> 03:27.931
STOP TALKING.
LOOK AT ME.

03:27.999 --> 03:30.165
I AM PLEASED TO ANNOUNCE

03:30.232 --> 03:33.331
THAT THIS YEAR
YOUR COMBINED TEAM G.P.A.

03:33.399 --> 03:36.631
IS THE HIGHEST
IN B.M.S. FOOTBALL HISTORY.

03:36.699 --> 03:37.931
WHAT´S A G.P.A.?

03:37.999 --> 03:39.632
WHO ARE YOU?

03:39.699 --> 03:41.098
I AM YOUR DEAN.

03:41.166 --> 03:42.366
OH.

03:42.432 --> 03:44.698
I´M LOOKING FOR ALEX MORAN.

03:44.766 --> 03:46.998
-UH-OH.
-RELAX.

03:47.066 --> 03:48.933
YOU´RE NOT BEING PUNISHED.

03:48.999 --> 03:50.532
YOU´RE BEING PUBLISHED.

03:50.599 --> 03:54.098
YOUR PAPER, "SUPERMAN´S BROTHER:
AN EXPANDED THEORY OF REALITY,"

03:54.166 --> 03:56.166
IS LIGHTING UP
THE ACADEMIC COMMUNITY.

03:56.232 --> 03:57.399
[ CHUCKLES ]
COOL.

03:57.466 --> 04:00.333
TELL ME, WITH ALL
OF YOUR PRACTICES,

04:00.399 --> 04:01.598
WHERE DID YOU FIND THE TIME

04:01.666 --> 04:04.366
TO WRITE SUCH A SOPHISTICATED
PIECE OF WORK?

04:04.432 --> 04:06.332
IT HAPPENED, I GUESS.

04:06.399 --> 04:09.431
WELL, WE ARE GOING TO BE GIVING
A BANQUET IN YOUR HONOR.

04:09.499 --> 04:10.731
AND...

04:11.999 --> 04:16.932
...YOU ARE GOING TO BE GIVING
A PRESENTATION ON THIS PAPER.

04:16.999 --> 04:19.666
YOU DID WRITE THE PAPER,
CORRECT?

04:19.732 --> 04:21.665
I MEAN, I´D HATE
TO FIND OUT OTHERWISE.

04:21.732 --> 04:25.332
YEAH, I-I ACCEPT YOUR PROPOSAL,
AND I´LL DO YOUR PRESENTATION.

04:25.399 --> 04:26.198
GREAT!

04:26.266 --> 04:27.598
-COOL.
-THAT´S IMPRESSIVE.

04:27.666 --> 04:29.499
IT´S NOT IMPRESSIVE.
HE DIDN´T DO SHIT.

04:29.566 --> 04:31.132
HIS NERD DID EVERYTHING FOR HIM.

04:31.199 --> 04:32.966
WAIT.
YOU GUYS GOT NERDS HERE?

04:33.032 --> 04:34.532
WE DON´T GOT THOSE IN DETROIT.

04:34.599 --> 04:37.366
EVERYBODY HAS THEIR OWN NERD
THAT DOES THEIR WORK FOR THEM,

04:37.432 --> 04:39.064
EVEN YOU.

04:40.399 --> 04:42.465
I HAVE MY OWN NERD?

04:42.532 --> 04:45.299
COACH, YOU SHOULD BE VERY PROUD
OF YOUR PLAYERS.

04:45.366 --> 04:47.132
SHUT UP AND GET OUT.

04:47.199 --> 04:50.499
[ Chanting ]
DO IT! DO IT! DO IT! DO IT!

04:50.566 --> 04:52.499
[ CHEERING ]

04:56.266 --> 04:58.066
GARY!
HEY, YOU MADE IT.

04:58.132 --> 04:59.198
THAT´S FOR YOU.

04:59.266 --> 05:00.333
WHAT´S THIS?

05:00.399 --> 05:03.565
OH, YOU KNOW THE PAPER YOU WROTE
CALLED "SUPERMAN´S BROTHER"?

05:03.632 --> 05:05.064
IT´S BEING PUBLISHED.

05:05.132 --> 05:06.132
NO WAY!

05:06.199 --> 05:07.332
YES WAY, YES.

05:07.399 --> 05:08.998
NOW I HAVE TO GIVE
A PRESENTATION

05:09.066 --> 05:10.966
AT A BANQUET IN MY HONOR,

05:11.032 --> 05:14.098
WHICH IS A LITTLE TOO MUCH
ATTENTION, IF YOU ASK ME.

05:14.166 --> 05:16.198
SO IF YOU COULD JUST EASE UP
ON THE EFFORT A LITTLE,

05:16.266 --> 05:17.366
-THAT´D BE GREAT.
-DON´T WORRY.

05:17.432 --> 05:18.998
I´LL TAKE CARE
OF THE PRESENTATION.

05:19.066 --> 05:20.132
THIS IS SO EXCITING.

05:20.199 --> 05:21.632
I KNOW.
I´M OVER THE MOON.

05:21.699 --> 05:24.931
HEY, WHICH ONE OF Y´ALL IN HERE
RADON RANDELL´S NERD?

05:24.999 --> 05:26.432
I KNOW Y´ALL HERE SOMEWHERE.

05:26.499 --> 05:29.332
OH, SHIT!
YOU´RE MY NERD!

05:29.399 --> 05:30.531
WHOO!

05:30.599 --> 05:32.665
I DIDN´T KNOW YOU EXISTED, MAN.

05:32.732 --> 05:34.532
I THOUGHT YOU WAS LIKE
THE TOOTH FAIRY OR SOMETHING,

05:34.599 --> 05:35.631
LIKE YOU´D JUST DO MY HOMEWORK

05:35.699 --> 05:37.566
AND THEN SLIDE IT UNDER
THE PROFESSOR´S PILLOW.

05:37.632 --> 05:38.964
-YOU KNOW WHAT I´M SAYING?
-NO.

05:39.032 --> 05:41.599
MY NERD!
MY NERD!

05:41.666 --> 05:43.566
I DONE FOUND -- I FOUND MY NERD!

05:43.632 --> 05:45.131
WE ABOUT TO GO GET DRUNK, MAN.
COME ON, MAN.

05:45.199 --> 05:46.632
YOU BELIEVE THIS SHIT?

05:46.699 --> 05:49.031
NERDS AND JOCKS
HANGING OUT TOGETHER.

05:49.099 --> 05:50.298
IT´S DISGUSTING.

05:50.366 --> 05:51.598
IT´S GROSS.

05:51.666 --> 05:53.232
YOU DO REALIZE
YOU´RE THE BIGGEST NERD

05:53.299 --> 05:54.966
AT THIS ENTIRE PARTY, RIGHT?

05:55.032 --> 05:57.399
♪ I´M THE BADDEST AROUND, YEAH ♪

05:57.466 --> 05:59.665
♪ ONE OF THE BADDEST AROUND ♪

05:59.732 --> 06:03.632
LABELS, MAN --
PEOPLE CALLING YOU A NERD,

06:03.699 --> 06:06.666
PEOPLE CALLING ME THE GREATEST
QUARTERBACK THAT EVER LIVED

06:06.732 --> 06:08.998
ON THE FACE OF THE PLANET
ON THE EARTH.

06:09.066 --> 06:10.666
WE JUST PEOPLE, MAN.

06:10.732 --> 06:12.298
AND WHEN WE DIE AND COME BACK,

06:12.366 --> 06:14.199
WE COME BACK
AS WHATEVER WE WANT.

06:14.266 --> 06:16.599
I´M GONNA COME BACK
AS A RARE FERRARI.

06:16.666 --> 06:18.232
I DON´T FEEL GOOD.

06:18.299 --> 06:19.232
GO TAKE A NAP.

06:19.299 --> 06:20.699
ANY BED YOU WANT.
IT´S ALL GOOD.

06:20.766 --> 06:23.065
HEY, YOU WANT ME TO SING TO YOU
OR SOME SHIT?

06:23.132 --> 06:25.065
I DON´T REALLY KNOW
HOW NERDS GO TO SLEEP.

06:25.132 --> 06:26.632
NO, THAT´S ALL RIGHT.

06:26.699 --> 06:28.131
[ GROANS ]

06:28.199 --> 06:30.666
[ LAUGHS ]

06:30.732 --> 06:32.331
I LOVE YOU, MY NERD BROTHER.

06:32.399 --> 06:34.031
LOVE YOU TOO, RADON.

06:37.199 --> 06:39.398
♪ I´M THE BADDEST AROUND ♪

06:46.466 --> 06:47.466
[ GRUNTS ]

06:49.032 --> 06:50.398
[ CHUCKLES ]

06:50.466 --> 06:52.565
THIS IS A WATERBED.

06:52.632 --> 06:54.231
[ DOOR CREAKS ]

07:04.732 --> 07:07.331
[ LAUGHS ]

07:07.399 --> 07:09.366
BEST PRANK EVER.

07:09.432 --> 07:11.464
YOU´RE GONNA BE SO WET.

07:13.032 --> 07:15.499
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

07:15.566 --> 07:19.132
WHOA, SO WHAT HAPPENED
TO NO MORE PARTYING?

07:19.199 --> 07:22.365
ALEX, I HAVE MONTHS OF WORK
TO CATCH UP ON.

07:22.432 --> 07:23.999
WEED HELPS ME FOCUS.

07:24.066 --> 07:25.499
AAH! OH, MY GOD!

07:25.566 --> 07:26.499
MY WATERBED!

07:26.566 --> 07:28.198
-MY FRIEND!
-MY NERD!

07:28.266 --> 07:31.199
MAN, SOMEBODY DROWNED MY NERD.

07:31.266 --> 07:33.699
[ GASPS ]

07:35.766 --> 07:38.198
THERE´S NO PERMANENT DAMAGE,

07:38.266 --> 07:40.633
BUT THERE´S NO TELLING
HOW LONG THE COMA WILL LAST.

07:40.699 --> 07:42.031
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

07:48.699 --> 07:52.098
IT´S JUST SOMETHING
TO REMEMBER HIM BY.

07:52.166 --> 07:56.198
NERDS, WE GOT YOU THIS.

07:56.266 --> 07:57.966
NO?

07:58.032 --> 07:59.499
MAYBE LATER.

08:01.166 --> 08:03.398
WE ARE VERY TRULY SORRY
FOR YOUR LOSS.

08:03.466 --> 08:05.366
WE KNOW THAT YOU´RE HURTING
RIGHT NOW.

08:05.432 --> 08:08.999
SO PLEASE FEEL FREE TO TAKE ONE
BONUS DAY OFF OF OUR HOMEWORK.

08:09.066 --> 08:11.398
BUT IT´S STILL DUE THIS WEEK,
THOUGH, SO IF --

08:11.466 --> 08:13.299
WHICH ONE OF YOU NEANDERTHALS
DID THIS?

08:13.366 --> 08:15.266
HEY, WE´RE ALL HURTING
RIGHT NOW.

08:15.332 --> 08:16.332
I MEAN, LOOK AT ME.

08:16.399 --> 08:19.431
I HAVE TO SLEEP IN LARRY´S
WATERBED UNTIL MINE GETS FIXED.

08:19.499 --> 08:20.598
THERE´S PAIN EVERYWHERE.

08:20.666 --> 08:21.633
THAT´S IT.

08:21.699 --> 08:24.566
I´M SICK OF US BEING TREATED
AS SECOND-CLASS CITIZENS.

08:24.632 --> 08:25.498
WHOA.

08:25.566 --> 08:28.032
WE WILL NEVER DO YOUR HOMEWORK
EVER AGAIN.

08:28.099 --> 08:28.498
WHAT?

08:28.566 --> 08:31.065
I DON´T CARE HOW MUCH
IT ALMOST GETS US LAID.

08:31.132 --> 08:33.164
NERDS, MAKE IT SO.

08:33.232 --> 08:35.298
THERE´S A PROTRACTOR IN THERE!

08:35.366 --> 08:38.033
[ ROCK MUSIC PLAYING ]

08:38.099 --> 08:40.032
[ KNOCKING ON DOOR ]

08:40.099 --> 08:40.766
[ DOOR OPENS ]

08:43.432 --> 08:45.399
YOU USED TO BE SMART, RIGHT?

08:45.466 --> 08:46.533
YEAH.

08:46.599 --> 08:47.532
GOOD.

08:47.599 --> 08:50.231
I HAVE A PRESENTATION
I HAVE TO GIVE TOMORROW

08:50.299 --> 08:53.465
ON A PAPER I DIDN´T EVEN WRITE
CALLED "SUPERMAN´S BROTHER."

08:53.533 --> 08:55.199
SUPERMAN DIDN´T HAVE A BROTHER.

08:55.266 --> 08:57.133
THAT´S WHAT THOUGHT, TOO!
I´M SO CONFUSED.

08:57.199 --> 08:59.032
I HAVEN´T EVEN READ THE PAPER.
I CAN´T GET THE PAPER.

08:59.099 --> 09:00.032
NOBODY WANTS TO GIVE ME
THE PAPER.

09:00.099 --> 09:01.032
THEY DON´T WANT TO EXPLAIN
THE PAPER.

09:01.099 --> 09:02.465
THEY DON´T EXPLAIN
WHAT´S IN THE BOX.

09:02.532 --> 09:04.032
WHAT IS THIS?
LOOK.

09:04.099 --> 09:05.398
"BLACK POWER"?
REALLY?

09:05.466 --> 09:06.666
I HAVE NO IDEA WHAT TO DO.

09:06.732 --> 09:08.064
ALEX!

09:08.132 --> 09:10.999
RELAX.
YOU JUST NEED TO FOCUS.

09:11.066 --> 09:13.265
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

09:13.332 --> 09:15.999
I´LL PACK MY BONG.

09:16.066 --> 09:17.666
SO, WHAT DO WE DO NOW?

09:17.732 --> 09:19.498
I´VE GOT
HEURISTICS HOMEWORK DUE.

09:19.566 --> 09:21.432
I DON´T EVEN KNOW
WHAT HEURISTICS IS.

09:21.499 --> 09:23.132
WE´LL JUST GET SOME NEW NERDS.

09:23.199 --> 09:24.531
YOU KNOW HOW MANY
GO TO THIS SCHOOL?

09:24.599 --> 09:25.665
LITERALLY BILLIONS.

09:27.132 --> 09:29.164
AH, WHAT THE HELLSIES?!

09:29.232 --> 09:30.999
TROT EVANS?

09:31.066 --> 09:33.165
WHAT ARE YOU BASEBALL GOONS
DOING ON OUR TURF?

09:33.232 --> 09:34.165
YOU KNOW THE RULES.

09:34.232 --> 09:35.331
YEAH, WELL, THE RULES CHANGED

09:35.399 --> 09:37.299
WHEN OUR NERDS
STOPPED DOING OUR HOMEWORK, BRO.

09:37.366 --> 09:38.966
SO NOW YOU´RE GONNA DO IT.

09:39.032 --> 09:40.064
THE BASEBALL TEAM´S NERDS

09:40.132 --> 09:41.231
STOPPED DOING HOMEWORK,
TOO, BRO?

09:41.299 --> 09:42.599
IT´S CAMPUS-WIDE, BRO.

09:42.666 --> 09:45.232
EVERY NERD ON THIS CAMPUS
IS ON STRIKE.

09:45.299 --> 09:46.099
BRO?

09:46.166 --> 09:47.532
-BRO.
-BRO.

09:47.599 --> 09:49.599
THIS IS WAY MORE SERIOUS
THAN I THOUGHT.

09:49.666 --> 09:53.232
I´M CALLING A MEETING
OF THE B.M.S. CAPTAINS.

09:53.299 --> 09:56.266
[ BELL TOLLING ]

09:56.332 --> 09:58.965
CAPTAINS OF B.M.S.,

09:59.032 --> 10:01.498
YOU ARE ALL AWARE
OF THE CURRENT NERD CRISIS.

10:01.566 --> 10:03.633
IF THIS ISN´T RESOLVED
IMMEDIATELY,

10:03.699 --> 10:06.065
WE MIGHT ALL
BE DOING OUR HOMEWORK.

10:06.132 --> 10:09.464
I´D LIKE TO OPEN THE FLOOR
TO ANY SOLUTIONS YOU MAY HAVE.

10:10.732 --> 10:11.699
[ SIGHS ]

10:11.766 --> 10:13.465
BRYCE WOODSY, TENNIS TEAM.

10:13.532 --> 10:16.099
WILL THERE AT ANY TIME
BE FOOD HERE?

10:17.266 --> 10:20.133
UM, YEAH, I THINK WE HAVE
SOME FOOD COMING, BRYCE.

10:20.199 --> 10:23.166
I THINK WE HAVE A NICE PLATTER
OF KNUCKLE SANDWICHES.

10:23.232 --> 10:24.199
DO YOU WANT ONE?

10:24.266 --> 10:26.166
WOULD YOU LIKE
A KNUCKLE SANDWICH?

10:26.232 --> 10:28.199
-I´M GOOD.
-THAT´S WHAT THOUGHT.

10:28.266 --> 10:31.598
NOW, DOES ANYONE
HAVE ANY SOLUTIONS?

10:31.666 --> 10:34.432
LUCY WILLIAMS, VOLLEYBALL.

10:34.499 --> 10:36.999
I WAS TOLD THIS MEETING
WAS FOR SPORTS CAPTAINS,

10:37.066 --> 10:38.999
SO WHY IS GOLF HERE?

10:39.066 --> 10:41.432
HEY, GOLF IS A SPORT.

10:41.499 --> 10:42.598
[ LAUGHTER ]

10:42.666 --> 10:43.932
IT´S A HOBBY.

10:43.999 --> 10:44.932
IT´S MORE LIKE CHESS
OR CHECKERS.

10:44.999 --> 10:45.999
IT´S NOT A SPORT.

10:46.066 --> 10:49.666
GUYS!
THE NERD CRISIS!

10:49.732 --> 10:51.998
[ French accent ]
CLAUDE CHAVALIER, HOCKEY TEAM.

10:52.066 --> 10:56.933
WHY DO NOT WE JUST PRESENT
THE NERDS AN OPTION OF --

10:56.999 --> 10:59.065
I DON´T UNDERSTAND A WORD
YOU´RE SAYING, BRO.

10:59.132 --> 11:00.298
LIKE NOT EVEN A LITTLE BIT.

11:00.366 --> 11:01.498
[ SPEAKS FRENCH ]

11:01.566 --> 11:03.133
NOT A WORD.

11:03.199 --> 11:06.565
-I DIDN´T -- DOES ANY -- CAN--
-[ SQUEAKING ]

11:10.499 --> 11:14.399
SAMMY CACCIATORE, SPIRIT SQUAD.

11:14.466 --> 11:17.066
MY SOLUTION -- PRANKING.

11:17.132 --> 11:18.498
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU, BRO?

11:18.566 --> 11:21.566
I´M THE JOCK
WHO PUT THAT NERD IN A COMA.

11:21.632 --> 11:23.499
THAT´S WHO AM, TOUGH GUY.

11:23.566 --> 11:24.598
THAT WAS YOU?

11:24.666 --> 11:25.633
